data.description: Investors Alert! Location, Location, Location!  Right off of 10th St and La Vista !  Incredible opportunity to own an 8 bedroom, 4 bathroom multi-family unit located on 818 Walnut Ave in McAllen, Texas. This could be used as an owner occupied investment or short /long term rentals ! This Multi Property features 4 parking spots and is perfect for those looking to generate rental income. Don’t miss out on this great opportunity! Contact us today to book a viewing.
